      "officialTitle": "The T-REX-Trial: Tailored Regional External Beam Radiotherapy in Clinically Node-negative Breast Cancer Patients With 1-2 Sentinel Node Macrometastases; an Open, Multicenter, Randomized Non-inferiority Phase 3-trial.",
